{"word":"H4186 - מֹושָׁב - môwshâb - mo-shawb' - Assembly","slug":"H4186","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מֹושָׁב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>môwshâb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mo-shawb'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Assembly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1; - mo&#x0302;sha&#x0302;b  mo&#x0302;sha&#x0302;b</b> - <i>mo-shawb', mo-shawb'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3427\">H3427</a>; a <i>seat</i>; figuratively a <i>site</i>; abstractly a <i>session</i>; by extension an <i>abode</i> (the place or the time); by implication <i>population: - </i>assembly, dwell in, dwelling (-place), wherein (that) dwelt (in), inhabited place, seat, sitting, situation, sojourning."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3143\">H3143</a>, <a href=\"#/H3427\">H3427</a>, <a href=\"#/H3428\">H3428</a>, <a href=\"#/H3429\">H3429</a>, <a href=\"#/H3430\">H3430</a>, <a href=\"#/H3436\">H3436</a>, <a href=\"#/H7675\">H7675</a>, <a href=\"#/H7871\">H7871</a>, <a href=\"#/H8453\">H8453</a>"}]}